data.name: Label17.Text
data.value: Minimal User Interaction is developed as a interaction guideline along with Softview GUI. Minimal User Interaction ensure that the user interaction is as simple as possible and with easy learning curve for difficult software interfaces. Uses same license as Softview GUI. Work with Softview GUI v2.3 and above

data.name: Label14.Text
data.value: Softview is a interface developed as open source by Arvin Soft for Sys Optimizer. The interface also uses the same license as sys optimizer the Softview interface is optimized to work on any window sizes from 1024 x 768 to 1920 x 1080. Fully Optimized for TouchScreens
